---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;

const SITE_URL = 'https://agentrank-ai.com';
---

<Base
  title="Quick Start — AgentRank API"
  description="Make your first AgentRank API call in under 5 minutes. No API key required for free tier access."
  keywords="AgentRank API quickstart, MCP API tutorial, agent tools API"
  canonicalUrl={`${SITE_URL}/docs/quickstart/`}
  activeTab="api"
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/docs/">Docs</a> / Quick Start</div>
    <h1>Quick Start</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your first API call in under 5 minutes. No account or key required to start.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="docs-nav">
    <a href="/docs/">Overview</a>
    <a href="/docs/quickstart/" class="active">Quick Start</a>
    <a href="/docs/authentication/">Auth</a>
    <a href="/docs/rate-limits/">Rate Limits</a>
    <a href="/docs/api/">API Reference</a>
    <a href="/docs/sdk/">SDK</a>
    <a href="/docs/embed/">Embed</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="step" id="step1">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-num">1</span>
      <h2>Search the index</h2>
    </div>
    <p>The search endpoint is public — no key needed. Query for any tool, skill, or agent topic:</p>
    <div class="code-block-wrap">
      <div class="code-label">curl</div>
      <pre class="code-block">curl "https://agentrank-ai.com/api/v1/search?q=filesystem&limit=3"</pre>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-copy={`curl "https://agentrank-ai.com/api/v1/search?q=filesystem&limit=3"`}>Copy</button>
    </div>
    <div class="response-block">
      <div class="code-label response-label">Response</div>
      <pre class="code-block response-code">{`{
  "query": "filesystem",
  "category": "all",
  "sort": "score",
  "results": [
    {
      "type": "tool",
      "id": "modelcontextprotocol--servers",
      "name": "modelcontextprotocol/servers",
      "description": "Model Context Protocol servers",
      "score": 97.4,
      "rank": 1,
      "url": "https://agentrank-ai.com/tool/modelcontextprotocol--servers/"
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "total": 48, "limit": 3, "offset": 0 }
}`}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="step" id="step2">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-num">2</span>
      <h2>Get a specific tool</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Look up any indexed tool by its GitHub <code>owner/repo</code>. Replace <code>/</code> with <code>--</code> in the URL:</p>
    <div class="code-block-wrap">
      <div class="code-label">curl</div>
      <pre class="code-block">curl "https://agentrank-ai.com/api/v1/tool/modelcontextprotocol--servers"</pre>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="curl &quot;https://agentrank-ai.com/api/v1/tool/modelcontextprotocol--servers&quot;">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <p>The response includes the score, rank, signals breakdown, and raw GitHub data.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="step" id="step3">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-num">3</span>
      <h2>Use the SDK (optional)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Install the TypeScript client to skip manual URL construction:</p>
    <div class="code-block-wrap">
      <div class="code-label">npm</div>
      <pre class="code-block">npm install @agentrank/sdk</pre>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="npm install @agentrank/sdk">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block-wrap" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
      <div class="code-label">TS</div>
      <pre class="code-block multiline">{`import { AgentRank } from '@agentrank/sdk';

const ar = new AgentRank(); // no key = free tier

const results = await ar.search('filesystem', { limit: 5 });
console.log(results.results[0].name, results.results[0].score);

const tool = await ar.getTool('modelcontextprotocol/servers');
console.log(tool.rank, tool.signals);`}</pre>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-copy={`import { AgentRank } from '@agentrank/sdk';\n\nconst ar = new AgentRank();\n\nconst results = await ar.search('filesystem', { limit: 5 });\nconsole.log(results.results[0].name, results.results[0].score);\n\nconst tool = await ar.getTool('modelcontextprotocol/servers');\nconsole.log(tool.rank, tool.signals);`}>Copy</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="step" id="step4">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-num">4</span>
      <h2>Get an API key for more</h2>
    </div>
    <p>The free tier gives you 100 req/min per IP with no key. A Pro key unlocks:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>10,000 requests/day</li>
      <li>Rank history on every tool — 30-day trend</li>
      <li>Batch lookup: resolve 50 tools in one request</li>
      <li>Access to v2 endpoints with additional fields</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Get a key at <a href="/pricing/">agentrank-ai.com/pricing/</a>. Keys look like <code>ark_pro_...</code></p>
    <div class="code-block-wrap" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
      <div class="code-label">TS</div>
      <pre class="code-block multiline">{`import { AgentRank } from '@agentrank/sdk';

const ar = new AgentRank({ apiKey: 'ark_pro_your_key_here' });

// Now using v2 — includes rankHistory
const tool = await ar.getTool('modelcontextprotocol/servers');
console.log(tool.rankHistory); // 30-day rank trend`}</pre>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-copy={`import { AgentRank } from '@agentrank/sdk';\n\nconst ar = new AgentRank({ apiKey: 'ark_pro_your_key_here' });\n\nconst tool = await ar.getTool('modelcontextprotocol/servers');\nconsole.log(tool.rankHistory);`}>Copy</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="next-steps">
    <h2>Next steps</h2>
    <div class="next-grid">
      <a href="/docs/api/" class="next-card">
        <div class="next-title">API Reference</div>
        <div class="next-desc">All endpoints, parameters, and response shapes.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/sdk/" class="next-card">
        <div class="next-title">SDK Reference</div>
        <div class="next-desc">Full TypeScript SDK documentation.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/authentication/" class="next-card">
        <div class="next-title">Authentication</div>
        <div class="next-desc">Key formats, headers, and tier differences.</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.copy-btn').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const text = btn.dataset.copy || btn.previousElementSibling?.textContent || '';
        if (!text) return;
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(text.trim()).then(() => {
          const orig = btn.textContent;
          btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
          setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = orig; }, 2000);
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .docs-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .docs-nav a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .docs-nav a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .docs-nav a.active { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

  .divider {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .step { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 1.75rem;
    height: 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #000;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  p code {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .code-block-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .code-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
    width: 3rem;
  }

  .code-block {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .code-block.multiline {
    white-space: pre;
    overflow-x: auto;
    text-overflow: unset;
  }

  .copy-btn {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.45rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: inherit;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .copy-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }

  .response-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .response-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .response-code {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    white-space: pre;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', monospace;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .next-steps { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .next-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .next-card {
    display: block;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .next-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }

  .next-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .next-desc {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
